	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بَلۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> بَدَا لَهُم مَّا كَانُواْ يُخۡفُونَ مِن قَبۡلُۖ وَلَوۡ رُدُّواْ لَعَادُواْ لِمَا نُهُواْ </div><div>عَنۡهُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَإِنَّهُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَكَٰذِبُونَ ٨٢ وَقَالُوٓاْ إِنۡ هِيَ إِلَّا حَيَاتُنَا ٱلدُّنۡيَا وَمَا </div><div>نَحۡنُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِمَبۡعُوثِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٩٢ وَلَوۡ تَرَىٰٓ إِذۡ <a data-content='حُبسوا على حُكمه تعالى للسّؤال' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وُقِفُواْ عَلَىٰ رَبِّهِمۡۚ</a> قَالَ أَلَيۡسَ </div><div>هَٰذَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِٱلۡحَقِّۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> قَالُواْ بَلَىٰ وَرَبِّنَاۚ قَالَ فَذُوقُواْ ٱلۡعَذَابَ بِمَا كُنتُمۡ </div><div>تَكۡفُرُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٠٣</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> قَدۡ خَسِرَ ٱلَّذِينَ كَذَّبُواْ بِلِقَآءِ ٱللَّهِۖ حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا جَآءَتۡهُمُ </div><div>ٱلسَّاعَةُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='فجأة من غير شعور' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>بَغۡتَةٗ</a> قَالُواْ يَٰحَسۡرَتَنَا عَلَىٰ مَا </div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'><a data-content='قصّرنا وضيّعنا في الحياة الدّنيا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>فَرَّطۡنَا فِيهَا</a> وَهُمۡ يَحۡمِلُونَ </div><div><a data-content='ذنوبهم وخطاياهم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>أَوۡزَارَهُمۡ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>عَلَىٰ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ظُهُورِهِمۡۚ أَلَا سَآءَ مَا يَزِرُونَ ١٣ وَمَا ٱلۡحَيَوٰةُ </div><div>ٱلدُّنۡيَآ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>إِلَّا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَعِبٞ وَلَهۡوٞۖ وَلَلدَّارُ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ لِّلَّذِينَ يَتَّقُونَۚ أَفَلَا </div><div>تَعۡقِلُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٢٣</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> قَدۡ نَعۡلَمُ إِنَّهُۥ لَيَحۡزُنُكَ ٱلَّذِي يَقُولُونَۖ فَإِنَّهُمۡ لَا </div><div>يُكَذِّبُونَكَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَٰكِنَّ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ بِ‍َٔايَٰتِ ٱللَّهِ يَجۡحَدُونَ ٣٣ وَلَقَدۡ </div><div>كُذِّبَتۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>رُسُلٞ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مِّن قَبۡلِكَ فَصَبَرُواْ عَلَىٰ مَا كُذِّبُواْ وَأُوذُواْ حَتَّىٰٓ </div><div>أَتَىٰهُمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>نَصۡرُنَاۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَلَا مُبَدِّلَ <a data-content='آيات وعده بنصر رسله' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>لِكَلِمَٰتِ ٱللَّهِۚ</a> وَلَقَدۡ جَآءَكَ مِن نَّبَإِيْ </div><div>ٱلۡمُرۡسَلِينَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٤٣</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَإِن كَانَ <a data-content='شقّ وعظُم عليك' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>كَبُرَ عَلَيۡكَ</a> إِعۡرَاضُهُمۡ فَإِنِ ٱسۡتَطَعۡتَ أَن </div><div>تَبۡتَغِيَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='سربا فيها ينفذ إلى ما تحتها' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>نَفَقٗا فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ</a> أَوۡ سُلَّمٗا فِي ٱلسَّمَآءِ فَتَأۡتِيَهُم بِ‍َٔايَةٖۚ وَلَوۡ شَآءَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'></div><div>شَآءَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱللَّهُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَجَمَعَهُمۡ عَلَى ٱلۡهُدَىٰۚ فَلَا تَكُونَنَّ مِنَ ٱلۡجَٰهِلِينَ </div><div>٥٣</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
